SUMMARY OF DATA CARDS FOR NASA/AMES WING-BODY PROGRAM
  1  Test case for comparison with the wind tunnel investigation reported                                                                
  2  in NASA TN D-7505, "Effect of Canard Location and Size on Canard-Wing                                                               
  3  Interference...." by Blair Gloss, NASA Langley Research Center                                                                      
  4  This case is with the canard OFF.                                                                                                   
  5  All dimensions are in cm.                                                                                                           
  6  Note that we are trying to match the wind tunnel Reynolds number                                                                    
  7  of 1.61E6  for skin friction calculations. Since cbar=23.31, the                                                                    
  8  value of rnl is 1.61E6/23.31=69E3                                                                                                   
  9                                                                                                                                      
 10  NASA TN D-7505 CONFIG BW1 60deg WING, CANARD OFF                                                                                    
 11   &BODY  bcode=0, oc=3,                                                                                                              
 12          lnose=14, lbody=96.52, ltail=0, radius=3.81,                                                                                
 13          xstart=47.65, nrows=8, nb=3,                                                                                                
 14          refmom=59.14, cbar=23.31, sref=1032.2,                                                                                      
 15          rnl=69000,                                                                                                                  
 16          mach=1.2,                                                                                                                   
 17   &END                                                                                                                               
 18                                                                                                                                      
 19   &WING  rootle=47.65, rootte=77.45, rooty=3.81,                                                                                     
 20          tiple=85.04,  tipte= 91.81, tipy=25.4,                                                                                      
 21          tcroot=0.06, tctip=0.04,                                                                                                    
 22   &END                                                                                                                               
 23                                                                                                                                      
 24   &AERO  CASE=2,&END                                                                                                                 
 25   &INCR  DELTA=2,&END                                                                                                                
 26   &INCR  DELTA=2,&END                                                                                                                
 27   &INCR  DELTA=2,&END                                                                                                                
 28                                                                                                                                      
END OF DATA CARDS 



